dsDescriptionValue.value: Two underlying datasets for a longitudinal cohort study evaluating the effectiveness of an mHealth application on quality of care and health outcomes for patients in primary health care facilities in Lebanon serving Syrian refugees and host communities. One file includes data obtained from patient exit interviews and the other from patient record reviews.
